flowchart TD
    classDef event fill:#ff9800,stroke:#e65100,color:#000
    classDef command fill:#2196f3,stroke:#0d47a1,color:#fff
    classDef actor fill:#ffeb3b,stroke:#f57f17,color:#000
    classDef system fill:#9c27b0,stroke:#4a148c,color:#fff
    classDef aggregate fill:#4caf50,stroke:#1b5e20,color:#fff
    classDef hotspot fill:#f44336,stroke:#b71c1c,color:#fff

    DataEng[数据工程师]:::actor
    Annotator[标注员\n内部/外包]:::actor
    Reviewer[审核员]:::actor
    AnnoTool[标注工具\n前端 Web App]:::system

    %% ── 任务配置 ──
    CmdDefineTask[定义标注任务\n类型/Episodes/时间窗口\n标注指南/截止日期]:::command
    EvtTaskDefined[标注任务已定义]:::event
    AggTask[AnnotationTask\nid / type / episodes\nguideline / deadline\nstatus / assignee]:::aggregate

    DataEng --> CmdDefineTask
    CmdDefineTask --> EvtTaskDefined
    EvtTaskDefined --> AggTask

    %% ── 分配 ──
    CmdAssign[分配给标注员\n支持手动/自动轮询]:::command
    EvtAssigned[任务已分配]:::event
    HotAssign[? 自动分配策略:\n负载均衡? 技能匹配?]:::hotspot

    AggTask --> CmdAssign
    DataEng --> CmdAssign
    CmdAssign --> EvtAssigned
    EvtAssigned -.question.- HotAssign
    EvtAssigned --> Annotator

    %% ── 标注执行 ──
    CmdLoadData[加载任务数据\n流式读取指定时间段]:::command
    EvtDataLoaded[数据已加载到标注工具]:::event
    CmdAnnotate[执行标注\n2D框/关键点/片段标记/多模态关联]:::command
    EvtDraftSaved[草稿已保存]:::event
    CmdSubmit[提交标注]:::command
    EvtSubmitted[标注已提交\n等待审核]:::event
    AggAnnotation[Annotation\nid / task_id / episode_id\ntime_range / labels\nannotator_id / version]:::aggregate

    Annotator --> CmdLoadData
    CmdLoadData --> EvtDataLoaded
    EvtDataLoaded --> AnnoTool
    AnnoTool --> CmdAnnotate
    CmdAnnotate --> EvtDraftSaved
    EvtDraftSaved -->|继续标注| CmdAnnotate
    Annotator --> CmdSubmit
    CmdSubmit --> EvtSubmitted
    EvtSubmitted --> AggAnnotation

    %% ── 审核 ──
    CmdStartReview[开始审核]:::command
    EvtReviewStarted[审核已开始]:::event
    CmdApprove[通过标注]:::command
    CmdReject[驳回标注\n附反馈意见]:::command
    EvtApproved[标注已通过\n→ 可纳入数据集]:::event
    EvtRejected[标注已驳回\n→ 返回修改]:::event

    Reviewer --> CmdStartReview
    AggAnnotation --> CmdStartReview
    CmdStartReview --> EvtReviewStarted
    Reviewer --> CmdApprove
    Reviewer --> CmdReject
    CmdApprove --> EvtApproved
    CmdReject --> EvtRejected
    EvtRejected -->|重新分配| CmdAssign

    %% ── 质控聚合 ──
    EvtIAAComputed[标注一致性计算完成\nInter-Annotator Agreement]:::event
    HotIAA[? IAA 是否必要?\n当前外包规模多大?]:::hotspot

    EvtApproved --> EvtIAAComputed
    EvtIAAComputed -.question.- HotIAA
